1 0 0 1 50 710 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 696 Tm (- public read access to station, route, incident, and analytics data) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 682 Tm (- admin-only write access for reference data) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 668 Tm (- controlled incident CRUD for authenticated users and operators) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 654 Tm (- analytics computed from locally stored relational data) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 640 Tm () Tj
