1 0 0 1 50 570 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 556 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 542 Tm (Versioned API prefix:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 528 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 514 Tm (```text) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 500 Tm (/api/v1) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 486 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 472 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 458 Tm (## Authentication) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 444 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 430 Tm (Authentication uses the `X-API-Key` header.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 416 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 402 Tm (Roles:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 388 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 374 Tm (- admin: full reference-data writes and incident management) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 360 Tm (- operator: incident create/update/delete) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 346 Tm (- user: incident create only) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 332 Tm (- public: no header required for reads) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 318 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 304 Tm (Example:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 290 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 276 Tm (```http) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 262 Tm (X-API-Key: change-me-admin-key) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 248 Tm (```) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 234 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 220 Tm (## Error Conventions) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 206 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 192 Tm (Typical error codes:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 178 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 164 Tm (- `400` bad request for invalid payloads) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 150 Tm (- `401` missing or invalid API key) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 136 Tm (- `403` authenticated but insufficient permissions) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 122 Tm (- `404` resource not found) Tj
ET
